                   Red Hat Security Advisory

Synopsis:          Updated iptables packages are available
Advisory ID:       RHSA-2003:213-01
Issue date:        2003-08-25
Updated on:        2003-08-25
Product:           Red Hat Linux
Keywords:          
Cross references:  
Obsoletes:         
